snippet.title: Super Intern Story Announcement Trailer | Steam | Itch.io
snippet.description:
Super Intern Story is a fun little adventure about working as a monster in a video game. Wear different costumes, get slain by heroes all while getting yelled at by your boss! 
Discover the joys of working behind the scene — as an unpaid intern in the game industry!

Wishlist now on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1068410/Super_Intern_Story/

Join our Discord  https://discord.gg/g5SPngST44

More info at https://bluenoisegames.com
